summary: This is an email from March 3, 2021, containing a forwarded image file (IMG_2660.jpg) and a brief comment questioning the age of an individual referred to as 'Jane doe 15' in a collection from 2001. The sender expresses doubt about the stated age, suggesting the person was likely 16 or 17 at the time.
